headline: NVIDIA (NVDA) Partners with onsemi for 800V AI Data Center Power Revolution
summary: In the latest move, onsemi's collaboration with NVIDIA (NVDA) to enhance AI data centers marks a notable step in expanding its technology ecosystem. Over the last quarter, NVIDIA’s share price rose 62%, driven in part by this collaboration, as it aligns with NVIDIA's efforts to broaden its AI and data center capabilities. Additionally, NVIDIA's robust earnings report and strategic partnerships, including those in quantum computing and AI infrastructure, further supported this upward trend...
